ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
CONFIGURATION SECTION.
SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-370.
OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-370.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  WS-TEST-RESULT      PIC X(50) VALUE 'Test Not Run'.
01  WS-EXPECTED-OUTPUT  PIC X(100) VALUE 'gnozod yzal eht revo spmuj xof nworb kciuq ehT'.
01  WS-ACTUAL-OUTPUT    PIC X(100).
01  WS-INPUT-TEXT       PIC X(100) VALUE 'The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog'.
01  WS-COUNTER          PIC 9(5)  VALUE 0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PARA.
    DISPLAY 'Running Test for COBOL-AI-LLM-Framework...'.
    PERFORM INIT-LLM-FRAMEWORK.
    PERFORM TEST-PROCESS-INPUT-TEXT.
    PERFORM VERIFY-OUTPUT.
    DISPLAY 'Test Result: ' WS-TEST-RESULT.
    STOP RUN.

INIT-LLM-FRAMEWORK.
    DISPLAY 'Loading COBOL-AI-LLM-Framework...'.
    * Simulate framework initialization
    PERFORM DUMMY-WAIT.
    DISPLAY 'COBOL-AI-LLM-Framework Initialized Successfully'.

TEST-PROCESS-INPUT-TEXT.
    DISPLAY 'Processing Input Text through LLM...'.
    * Simulate text processing
    MOVE FUNCTION REVERSE(WS-INPUT-TEXT) TO WS-ACTUAL-OUTPUT.
    DISPLAY 'Actual Output: ' WS-ACTUAL-OUTPUT.

VERIFY-OUTPUT.
    IF WS-ACTUAL-OUTPUT = WS-EXPECTED-OUTPUT THEN
        MOVE 'Test Passed' TO WS-TEST-RESULT
    ELSE
        MOVE 'Test Failed' TO WS-TEST-RESULT
    END-IF.

DUMMY-WAIT.
    PERFORM VARYING WS-COUNTER FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-COUNTER > 5000
        CONTINUE
    END-PERFORM.

